--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ecacf7bdd7e77b2419e140cb5ded6aa5, type: 3}
  m_Name: KnotTextCollection_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Knot.Localization::Knot.Localization.Data.KnotTextCollection
  _items:
  - _key: Tut-line1
    _rawText: Well well well... looks like you bozos got sucked into this movie wasteland.
  - _key: Tut-line2
    _rawText: But I can get you out. Just protect me. Yeah, the VHS tape on the right.
      See me?
  - _key: Tut-line3
    _rawText: First off, let's try move with D-pad.
  - _key: Tut-line4
    _rawText: Good. See my health bar on top? Not great. HOLD A next to me to rewind
      = heal me. Thanks!
  - _key: Tut-line5
    _rawText: Monsters are coming for me soon. You can't punch 'em, so I got you
      a flamethrower.
  - _key: Tut-line6
    _rawText: Click A to grab it. Click A again to put it down (only on grass).
  - _key: Tut-line7
    _rawText: Nice! Now try Click B to spin it around.
  - _key: Tut-line8
    _rawText: Great. But you probably noticed... it ain't doing anything right now.
  - _key: Tut-line9
    _rawText: 'That''s cause time is the juice for these modules.  '
  - _key: Tut-line10
    _rawText: Try HOLDING A to rewind the module next to ya.
  - _key: Tut-line11
    _rawText: Now HOLD B to fast forward, shoots faster, burns out quicker.
  - _key: Tut-line12
    _rawText: If you're holding a module, you can't time-manipulate it yourself.
      But the other player can, just have them HOLD A or B while you hold it.
  - _key: Tut-line13
    _rawText: Awesome. There's actually another type of module, go grab it and place
      it on the grass first.
  - _key: Tut-line14
    _rawText: You can see it got the battery icon on top, that means it needs full
      time to wake up.
  - _key: Tut-line15
    _rawText: 'So here''s the move: HOLD A to rewind it full, then HOLD B to fire
      it up. Try that on the explosive tank.'
  - _key: Tut-line16
    _rawText: <b>BOOOOM BABY!!!</b>
  - _key: Tut-line17
    _rawText: Oh, and that car? Try rewind it, then fast forward it. (HOLD A, then
      HOLD B)
  - _key: Tut-line18
    _rawText: Uh-oh... incoming ugly! Something's coming for me! PROTECT YOUR TAPE,
      DUDE!
  - _key: Tut-line19
    _rawText: Not bad. I'll toss you more modules during the real fight. Now go kick
      butt. I'm counting on ya.
